{
  "stem": "14060.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That is, I think, the first time that I came across real atrocity which I personally witnessed has happened to the person.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I mean, I didn't see when they did it, but I saw it the aftereffects of it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it's interesting how-- I mean, I'm being of 66 years of age.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To the best of my knowledge, I don't suffer of amnesia, so I do remember many things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that is a particular picture which is clear in my own mind.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, it didn't happen to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It didn't happen to even a relation of mine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this commotion, where people were milling around, I think the praying on that Shabbat was equal to zero, or maybe some did better than others.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was like-- like a-- a refugee camp, it appeared to me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, matters seemed to have settled down, to the effect that many of them stayed in Sopron, in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The children quickly learned the language.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And very relatively poor condition, depending who there relations were.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And everybody tried to help them, whatever method.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because, I must say, the majority of the-- of the original Jewish population of the town were well-to-do.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were some poorer people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But you didn't see the poverty of Poland or Galicia or Russia in our town.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was no child who didn't have clothing or shoes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Maybe they didn't have from one week to the next more than what they could live on and they had to live on some sort of assistance of others.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I remember, when it came to Purim time, to-- the custom was to [NON-ENGLISH], that we had a plate, a dinner plate.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my mother was an excellent-- she was a Cordon Bleu baker and very good cook.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
